text: Jakub Kaczmarek (born 27 September 1993) is a Polish professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Continental team . ==Major results== ;2010 : 1st 20px Road race, National Junior Road Championships ;2015 : 8th Overall Course de Solidarnosc et des Champions Olympiques ;2018 : 8th Overall Tour of Malopolska : 9th International Race Grand Prix Doliny Baryczy Milicz : 10th Overall Course de Solidarnosc et des Champions Olympiques ;2020 : 1st 20px Overall Tour of Szeklerland ::1st Stage 2 : 1st 20px Overall Belgrade Banjaluka ::1st Stage 2 ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Kalisz
title: Jakub Kaczmarek
